title: 820-3209-A A1466 2012
message: Check S5_PWRGD, PM_DSW_PWRGD, PCH_DSWVRMEN and PM_BATLOW_L.

title: 820-3209-A A1466 2012
message:
PCH will not start power on sequence without correct PM_BATLOW_L.
Try to start with both charger and battery connected.
Battery is charged at least?

Be sure to have original Magsafe charger.
Also try to start in SMC bypass mode.
